## CI/CD

GitHub Actions runs on every push and pull request:

| Job | Trigger | Steps |
|-----|---------|-------|
| `lint` | push, PR | PHP-CS-Fixer check, PHPStan, Rector dry-run |
| `test` | push, PR | Composer install, DB setup, test suite |
| `security` | push, PR | `composer audit` for known CVEs |
| `build` | main branch | Production build verification |

All jobs must pass before merging to `main`.

